./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/research/research.md:59:- `tasks.md` should be rewritten from “call reducers and create new docs” into “wire config templates, command flags, synthesis steps, and existing synthesis docs.” In practice that means repointing `T013`-`T018` to `resourceMap.emit`, `--no-resource-map`, `state_paths.resource_map_output`, and `step_emit_resource_map`, while replacing `T025`-`T028` with edits to the existing synthesis feature-catalog and final-synthesis playbook files. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:61] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:63] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:73] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/deep-research.md:64] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:999] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/feature_catalog/01--loop-lifecycle/04-synthesis.md:18]
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/research/research.md:60:- `checklist.md` should stop validating the wrong failure model. Missing canonical iteration artifacts remain workflow hard failures, while degraded handling applies only to malformed non-canonical evidence rows; verification should also prove Note/Summary-based counts and the existing synthesis command/feature/playbook surfaces rather than custom columns or new standalone docs. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/checklist.md:55] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/checklist.md:71] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/assets/prompt_pack_iteration.md.tmpl:50] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:788] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/templates/resource-map.md:39]
