./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/research/findings-registry.json:442:      "text": "`spec.md` is no longer implementation-safe because its summary, handoff criteria, scope, and requirements still assume reducer-local ownership, nested `findings[]` extractor inputs, and custom `Findings` / `Citations` columns. The rewrite target is a workflow-owned `phase_synthesis` emission step that consumes delta JSONL streams and renders the existing `Path | Action | Status | Note` template without adding columns. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/spec.md:4] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/spec.md:50] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/spec.md:78] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/spec.md:135] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/assets/prompt_pack_iteration.md.tmpl:40] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/assets/prompt_pack_iteration.md.tmpl:67] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:827] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:999] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/templates/resource-map.md:37] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/templates/resource-map.md:67]",
