./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/research/findings-registry.json:475:      "text": "The file/change inventory in the packet is still too “new-surface” heavy for the live contract. The rewrite list should keep the shared extractor and command docs, add both config templates as explicit edit targets, keep the four YAML workflows as synthesis-step edits, and replace wildcard “create feature/playbook docs” language with edits to `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/feature_catalog/01--loop-lifecycle/04-synthesis.md`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/feature_catalog/01--loop-lifecycle/04-synthesis.md`, and the two final-synthesis playbook scenarios that currently only mention `research/research.md` or `review/review-report.md`. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/spec.md:100] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/spec.md:118] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/deep-research.md:183] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/deep-review.md:204] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/feature_catalog/01--loop-lifecycle/04-synthesis.md:18] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/feature_catalog/01--loop-lifecycle/04-synthesis.md:25] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/manual_testing_playbook/06--synthesis-save-and-guardrails/019-final-synthesis-memory-save-and-guardrail-behavior.md:31] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/manual_testing_playbook/06--synthesis-save-and-guardrails/027-final-synthesis-memory-save-and-guardrail-behavior.md:31]",
