./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/research/findings-registry.json:508:      "text": "The packet task plan is pointed at the wrong implementation seam. `T013`-`T018` still wire reducers and generic YAML edits, but the live contract requires top-level `resourceMap.emit` config plumbing, `--no-resource-map` command parsing, `state_paths.resource_map_output`, and a dedicated `step_emit_resource_map` inserted in synthesis after summary hydration and, in confirm mode, after the pre-synthesis gate but before narrative compilation. `T025`-`T028` should stop creating new wildcard docs and instead edit the existing synthesis feature-catalog and finalization playbook files already used as the operator-facing contract. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:58] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:61] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:63] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/tasks.md:73] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/deep-research.md:64] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/deep-review.md:62] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:831] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_confirm.yaml:975] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/feature_catalog/01--loop-lifecycle/04-synthesis.md:18] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/manual_testing_playbook/06--synthesis-save-and-guardrails/027-final-synthesis-memory-save-and-guardrail-behavior.md:26]",
