./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/research/findings-registry.json:541:      "text": "The verification checklist still encodes the stale behavior model. `CHK-011` should verify synthesis-step ordering instead of reducer-write races, `CHK-020`-`CHK-025` should verify Note/Summary-based counts plus the hard-failure boundary for missing canonical iteration artifacts, and `CHK-040`-`CHK-045` should cover the existing command, synthesis feature, and final-synthesis playbook surfaces rather than implying new standalone docs or template forks. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/checklist.md:55] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/checklist.md:66] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/checklist.md:69] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-resource-map-deep-loop-fix/003-resource-map-deep-loop-integration/checklist.md:89] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/templates/resource-map.md:39] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/templates/resource-map.md:45] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/assets/prompt_pack_iteration.md.tmpl:50] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:788] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/manual_testing_playbook/06--synthesis-save-and-guardrails/019-final-synthesis-memory-save-and-guardrail-behavior.md:26] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/manual_testing_playbook/06--synthesis-save-and-guardrails/027-final-synthesis-memory-save-and-guardrail-behavior.md:26]",
