./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/003-continuity-memory-runtime/003-continuity-refactor-gates/prompts/research-prompt-implementation.md:271:1. **`research/research.md`** — progressive synthesis. Opens with answers to all 9 key questions. Closes with the recommended design. Cites evidence with `file:line` throughout. Owned by the sk-deep-research workflow; refreshed each iteration.
