./.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/061-agent-optimization/008-agent-deep-review/improvement/candidates/iter-1-candidate-001.md:238:Create `review/iterations/iteration-NNN.md`. Use exactly one canonical template. The reducer at `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/scripts/reduce-state.cjs` reads both the legacy section names (`## Focus`, `## Findings`, `## Ruled Out`, `## Dead Ends`, `## Recommended Next Focus`, `## Assessment`) and the live section names below. Inside findings, use `### P0 Findings`, `### P1 Findings`, and `### P2 Findings` subsections. Findings use numbered bullets of the form `N. **Title** -- file:line -- Description`, each followed by a claim-adjudication JSON block for P0/P1.
