./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7700:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:216:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-502",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7701:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:226:      "id": "finding-2-3-the-deep-research-reducer-still-operates-on-iteration-markdown-sections-plus-jso",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7702:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:227:      "text": "The deep-research reducer still operates on iteration markdown sections plus JSONL rows filtered to `type === \"iteration\"`, then rebuilds packet outputs from those inputs; there is no reducer-owned path here that parses or promotes `graphEvents` into strategy, registry, or dashboard state. That means the synchronized packet surfaces remain blind to graph-aware stop evidence unless some other process reads the graph separately (.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:103-127; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-502).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7703:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:230:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:48-52",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7704:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:231:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/iterations/iteration-001.md:7-10",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7705:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:232:        ".opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:326",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7706:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:234:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:103-127",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7707:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:235:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-502",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7708:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:246:      "text": "The shared graph-convergence handler does implement real stop-gating against persisted graph state: it computes graph signals, then evaluates research/review blockers using `findCoverageGaps()`, `findContradictions()`, and `findUnverifiedClaims()` before returning `STOP_ALLOWED`, `STOP_BLOCKED`, or `CONTINUE` (.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/coverage-graph/convergence.ts:20-25; .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/coverage-graph/convergence.ts:109-163; .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/coverage-graph/convergence.ts:245-275; .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/coverage-graph/convergence.ts:343-355).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7709:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:249:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:48-52",
