./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7720:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:283:      "text": "`sk-deep-research`'s active reducer does not implement the shared-graph bridge: it only imports `node:fs` and `node:path`, and the only reducer references matching `graph|convergence|upsert|deep_loop` are pass-through reads of precomputed `convergenceSignals`, not graph parsing or MCP calls (.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:11-12; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:246-247; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:271; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:442).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7721:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:286:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:48-52",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7722:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:287:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/iterations/iteration-002.md:7-10",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7723:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:288:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:11-12",
