./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7729:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:306:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:11-12",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7730:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:307:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:1181-1205",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7731:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:311:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/002-semantic-coverage-graph/implementation-summary.md:47-55",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7732:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:319:      "text": "Both deep-loop convergence contracts still document a reducer-owned in-memory graph bridge that is not present in the live reducer: deep research says \"the reducer builds an in-memory coverage graph\" when `graphEvents` exist, and deep review says the same for review iterations (.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:1181-1205; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/references/convergence.md:658-683).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7733:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:322:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:48-52",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7734:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:323:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/iterations/iteration-002.md:7-10",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7735:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:324:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:11-12",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7736:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:325:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:1181-1205",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7737:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:329:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/002-semantic-coverage-graph/implementation-summary.md:47-55",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7738:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:337:      "text": "The 042 graph-integration packet explicitly recorded the intended bridge as already implemented: its implementation summary says the reducer parses `graphEvents`, calls `deep_loop_graph_upsert`, and falls back through `JSONL -> local JSON graph -> SQLite projection`, which sharpens this audit result into a current reality gap between packet claims and runtime wiring (.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/002-semantic-coverage-graph/implementation-summary.md:47-55).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7739:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:340:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:48-52",
