./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7745:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:359:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/iterations/iteration-002.md:7-10",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7746:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:360:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:11-12",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7747:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:361:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:1181-1205",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7748:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:365:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/002-semantic-coverage-graph/implementation-summary.md:47-55",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7749:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:372:      "id": "finding-4-2-sk-deep-research-s-persisted-lineage-metadata-stays-wired-to-fresh-session-defau",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7750:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:373:      "text": "`sk-deep-research`'s persisted lineage metadata stays wired to fresh-session defaults in the normal runtime path I inspected. The auto workflow seeds `lineage.lineageMode: \"new\"`, `lineage.parentSessionId: null`, and `lineage.continuedFromRun: null` during config creation (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:157-180`), then later uses a synthesis fallback of `'completed-continue'` if no stop reason is found (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:390-409`). The reducer's status view reads lifecycle mode only from `config.lineage.lineageMode`, while its JSONL load drops all non-`iteration` records (`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:405-414`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-490`). That means resume/reopen semantics can influence control flow without updating reducer-visible lineage state away from `new`.",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7751:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:376:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:44-47",
