./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7768:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:411:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:305-309",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7769:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:415:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:405-414",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7770:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:416:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-490",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7771:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:423:      "text": "Because both reducers collapse JSONL to iteration rows only, even a correctly emitted blocked-stop event would not survive into the synchronized dashboard/strategy surfaces without separate promotion logic. Deep research loads `parseJsonl(...).filter((record) => record.type === 'iteration')` before rendering status and metrics (`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:405-414`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-490`), and deep review derives both dashboard and status output from the same iteration-only view (`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:485-487`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:539-548`). So full `gateResults` and lifecycle events are currently dropped twice: first by the flat YAML outputs, then again by reducer ingestion rules.",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7772:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:426:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:44-47",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7773:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:427:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/iterations/iteration-003.md:38-39",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7774:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:428:        ".opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:128-180",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7775:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:429:        ".opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:390-445",
