./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7777:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:434:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/state_format.md:234-246",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7778:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:435:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:214-220",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7779:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:436:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:305-309",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7780:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:440:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:405-414",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7781:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:441:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-490",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7782:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:448:      "text": "The blocked-stop contract is much richer than the live workflow outputs. Deep research requires a replayable legal-stop bundle and says any failed gate must append a `blocked_stop` event carrying `stopReason: \"blockedStop\"`, `legalStop.blockedBy`, full `legalStop.gateResults`, and a `recoveryStrategy` (`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:214-220`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:305-309`). Deep review documents the same shape, including a full `gateResults` map and replay inputs (`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/references/convergence.md:58-85`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/references/convergence.md:411-411`). But the live auto workflows emit only `decision` plus a human-readable `reason` from convergence (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:268-286`, `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:356-372`), so the documented gate bundle never appears in the reducer-facing runtime outputs I inspected.",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7783:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:451:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:44-47",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7784:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:452:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/iterations/iteration-003.md:38-39",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7785:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:453:        ".opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:128-180",
