./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7787:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:458:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/loop_protocol.md:46-91",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7788:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:459:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/state_format.md:234-246",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7789:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:460:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:214-220",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7790:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:461:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:305-309",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7791:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:465:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:405-414",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7792:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:466:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-490",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7793:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:473:      "text": "The live auto workflows classify `resume`, `restart`, `fork`, and `completed-session`, but the active YAML evidence I inspected does not append first-class `resumed`, `restarted`, `forked`, or `completed_continue` events during those branches. In `sk-deep-research`, the runtime branches only log/skip (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:128-153`), while the only explicit event appends in the file are `migration`, `paused`, and `synthesis_complete` (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:126`, `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:244`, `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:445`). `sk-deep-review` shows the same pattern: lifecycle branches are classified (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:155-177`), but the concrete event appends I found are `migration`, `paused`, `stuck_recovery`, and `synthesis_complete` only (`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:149`, `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:329`, `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:382`, `.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml:661`).",
