./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7863:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:621:        ".opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-502",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7864:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:627:      "id": "finding-5-6-the-reducer-dashboard-layer-does-not-repair-that-drift-deep-research-filters-jso",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7865:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:628:      "text": "The reducer/dashboard layer does not repair that drift. Deep research filters JSONL down to `record.type === 'iteration'` before building registry/dashboard state and only exposes lifecycle metadata from config, while deep review renders dashboard progress from iteration rows and exposes lifecycle mode from config without surfacing any `stopReason` field. In practice, that means no reducer-owned surface normalizes or republishes `userPaused`, `blockedStop`, or `stuckRecovery` for downstream consumers (.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:407-414; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:489-502; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:484-548; .opencode/skills/sk-deep-review/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:625-638).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:7866:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:631:        ".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:44-47",
