./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8055:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:1498:        "`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:438-443`",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8056:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:1501:        "`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/references/convergence.md:1183-1205`",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8057:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:1503:        "`.opencode/commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml:322-331`",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8058:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:1508:      "id": "finding-14-3-the-shipped-deep-research-reducer-does-not-consume-either-of-those-graph-specifi",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8059:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:1509:      "text": "The shipped deep-research reducer does not consume either of those graph-specific outputs directly. Its registry `convergenceScore` is set from `latestIteration.convergenceSignals.compositeStop ?? latestIteration.newInfoRatio ?? 0`, and the trend block only prints that scalar plus `coverageBySources`. I found no reducer path in the inspected ranges that reads `graphScore`, `blendedScore`, or graph gate results, so graph math only reaches research state if some earlier producer already collapsed it into `convergenceSignals.compositeStop` (`.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:244-273`, `.opencode/skills/sk-deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs:438-443`).",
./.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-cleanup/003-mcp-runtime-stress-remediation/001-search-intelligence-stress-test/002-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8060:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/findings-registry.json:1512:        "`.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/research/deep-research-strategy.md:48-52`",
