esolveCopilotPromptArg still only chooses raw prompt versus @PROMPT_PATH and has no approved-folder or plan-only Gate 3 contract.","Q-P1 winner remains an isolated SPEC_KIT_DB_DIR degraded-graph harness because unit coverage already exercises all fallbackDecision branches while the stress gap was end-to-end degraded state.","Q-P2 winner is a new non-mutating getGraphReadinessSnapshot helper for code_graph_status; getGraphFreshness currently loses action/reason detail, while ensureCodeGraphReady is unsuitable because it caches, cleans deleted tracked files, and can index.","Do not lower file-watcher debounce first; existing debounce/write-stability/concurrency/dedupe behavior makes status action visibility the lower-risk first fix.","Q-ARCH should carry target-authority vs recovered-context and readiness-action vs freshness-label as the two scoped seams."],"timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:22:17Z"}
